[b]when ever i try to add something in autospawn[/b]

whenever i go to add a NPC into the autospawn.cfg of empirescape source, i compile and everything works..but when i run it, it says something weird..about the NPchandeler.java..and then i try to logg on andnothing loads..

@ModAssassin wrote:

[quote=“johno2, post:2, topic:285399”]When you added your NPC, when you went to the next part of code (where gaps are) did you use tab button? For some reason, when ever i use the space bar it doesn’t add the npc, so make sure you used TAB instead, (above Caps Lock)

Hope this helps
~Johno[/quote]

item.dc:creator: @johno2 johno2
item.description:
@johno2 wrote:

When you added your NPC, when you went to the next part of code (where gaps are) did you use tab button? For some reason, when ever i use the space bar it doesn’t add the npc, so make sure you used TAB instead, (above Caps Lock)

Hope this helps
~Johno
